accesscontrol-desc: Enables group access restriction on a page by user basis
accesscontrol-info: Please respect the copyright holder and do not redistribute content from these pages.
accesscontrol-info-box: Access restrictions were established for this page. If you see this message, you have no access to this page.
accesscontrol-wrong-group-title: Title '$1' provided as a group for the Access Control extension is wrong.
accesscontrol-group-does-not-exist: Title [[$1]] provided as a group for the Access Control extension does not exists.
